Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/toddasmith/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim ~/dotfiles/vim

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/dotfiles/vim/vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/dotfiles/vim/gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
